Eddie Kaye Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Kaye_Thomas 0 Eddie Kaye Thomas (born October 31, 1980) is an actor who rose to prominence as Paul Finch in the American Pie film series. He is also known for his roles as Andy Rosenberg in the Harold Kumar series and as Jeff Woodcock in 'Til Death. He also starred in the CBS show Scorpion as Dr. Tobias "Toby" Curtis.
